The paper also uses machine learning algorithms such as Logistic Regression, Naive Bayes, and Random Forest, which are commonly used in deep learning (DL) and machine learning (ML) research, making cs.DL a likely sub-category as well. The paper also deals with labeled datasets, which are commonly used in database (DB) research.
